{"tid":2291240,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"神秘美女竟成日本社長？台女神登日媒　不科學爆乳再掀熱議","createTime":"2020-11-18T15:12:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T15:24:24.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1c35af1d2e77a5d95c8f297bdf865cc298bbde95","tid":2291240,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T15:12:45.000Z","msg":"旅日人氣台籍女神潘家儀（Vanessa Pan／咖滋咪），過去以寫真女星身分出道，曾出過多張寫真DVD與寫真書的她擁有傲人好身材，讓她順利進軍日本，接下多項代言工作。現在更躍升成為社長，近日她登上日本雜誌《SPA！デジタル》以「神秘美女社長」（謎の美女は女社長）再度掀起話題。<br />\n<br />\n有「媚惑女王」稱號的潘家儀，2012年以文化大學第一名的優異成績，前往日本交換學生留學，過去在「無名小站」人氣就相當高，並成功在日本出道，不僅發售個人寫真，還代言多項遊戲作品。<br />\n<br />\n曾返台於西門町開設「夢幻莊園」女僕咖啡廳，近年來跨足區塊鏈、IT產業，搖身一變成多角經營的強人女社長，受到日本商界肯定。去年推出個人寫真DVD《 教教我 潘老師》（おしえて！パン先生），在亞馬遜、樂天、DMM飆入月銷售榜第一名，賣得比日本現役寫真女星還要好，關鍵字「ヴァネッサ・パン」更一舉躍上日本各大網站，打破「胸大無腦」迷思。<br />\n<br />\n清純甜美的外型，加上傲人上圍身材。讓日本雜誌《SPA！デジタル》特別以「美女社長」身分介紹潘家儀，更刊登她多張惹火性感寫真照，不但身兼寫真女星還多角經營，曾經經營過女僕咖啡廳的她，親自穿著爆乳女僕完全成為店花，更是目前在日本賣最好的台籍寫真女星，讓日本網友興奮喊，「好美的女社長！」"},{"pid":"0bd42c204bf4b4192e908b945e29680946a1dee7","tid":2291240,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T15:12:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/18/2889128-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F18%2F2889128-PH.jpg&h=8c399180&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼日媒以「神秘美女社長」介紹潘家儀。（圖／翻攝自kazuminoomi IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/18/2889147-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F18%2F2889147-PH.jpg&h=f0fcc0a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efeb8c547f3bcb2c1ed56b0e82aad80f69ba5f23","tid":2291240,"uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T15:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/18/2889138-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F18%2F2889138-PH.jpg&h=179cddef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼日媒揭露多張潘家儀穿著女社長寫真的性感照。（圖／翻攝自いーぐら！&trade; 公式推特）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/18/2889124-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F18%2F2889124-PH.jpg&h=86230347&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"269bce9f554c0b0ec796f746f1b40423891366ec","tid":2291240,"uid":16659,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T15:14:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/18/2889157-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F18%2F2889157-PH.jpg&h=6b598cc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲潘家儀親自穿著爆乳女僕完全成為店花。（圖／翻攝自kazuminoomi IG）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/09/09/2120427-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F09%2F09%2F2120427-PH.jpg&h=fdaec356&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲潘家儀擁傲人身材，成為日本網友心目中的完美女神。（圖／翻攝自kazuminoomi IG）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/10/17/2832155-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F10%2F17%2F2832155-PH.jpg&h=f64e5a15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲潘家儀是目前日本最受歡迎的台籍寫真女星。（圖／翻攝自kazuminoomi IG）"},{"pid":"18dab8c2edd36319258fa6831c3e02078be14f6b","tid":2291240,"uid":320204,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T15:19:41.000Z","msg":"一律建議下海<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b3220bc16ed04d36f8f60c128881d6400b00c9","tid":2291240,"uid":155818,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T15:20:30.000Z","msg":"屌那星對奶正能到"},{"pid":"7ff6211772b610567b117b52cc52cd85c0b41696","tid":2291240,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T15:22:28.000Z","msg":"我可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{